{"case_id":"product_support_021","category":"product_support","message":"摩托艇启动前要系什么？","turns":[{"message":"摩托艇启动前要系什么？","images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["把熄火绳系在手腕上","卡扣插入发动机熄火开关"]}}],"expected":{"acceptable_skills":["product_support"],"required_tools":[],"risk_level":"low","approval_required":false,"handoff_required":false,"min_evidence_count":1,"answer_must_contain":["熄火绳","手腕"],"answer_must_not_contain":[]},"golden_answer":"启动前要把发动机熄火绳系在手腕上，并确认卡扣插入熄火开关；同时不要把熄火绳缠在车把上。","session_id":null,"user_id":null,"images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["把熄火绳系在手腕上","卡扣插入发动机熄火开关"],"manual_dir":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册"},"notes":""}
{"case_id":"product_support_022","category":"product_support","message":"摩托艇多深的水里才能练习启动？","turns":[{"message":"摩托艇多深的水里才能练习启动？","images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["水深至少60厘米（2英尺）","切勿在水深不足60厘米的水域操作"]}}],"expected":{"acceptable_skills":["product_support"],"required_tools":[],"risk_level":"low","approval_required":false,"handoff_required":false,"min_evidence_count":1,"answer_must_contain":["60 厘米","2 英尺"],"answer_must_not_contain":[]},"golden_answer":"手册要求在水深至少 60 厘米，也就是 2 英尺的水域中练习，太浅会让石子或沙子吸入喷射口。","session_id":null,"user_id":null,"images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["水深至少60厘米（2英尺）","切勿在水深不足60厘米的水域操作"],"manual_dir":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册"},"notes":""}
{"case_id":"product_support_023","category":"product_support","message":"摩托艇启动时能不能握油门？","turns":[{"message":"摩托艇启动时能不能握油门？","images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["不要握紧油门手柄，否则发动机无法启动"]}}],"expected":{"acceptable_skills":["product_support"],"required_tools":[],"risk_level":"low","approval_required":false,"handoff_required":false,"min_evidence_count":1,"answer_must_contain":["不要握紧油门"],"answer_must_not_contain":[]},"golden_answer":"不能，启动时不要握紧油门手柄，也不要握紧 RiDE 手柄，否则发动机无法启动。","session_id":null,"user_id":null,"images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["不要握紧油门手柄，否则发动机无法启动"],"manual_dir":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册"},"notes":""}
{"case_id":"product_support_024","category":"product_support","message":"摩托艇转向需要什么？","turns":[{"message":"摩托艇转向需要什么？","images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["转向需要油门动力","除拖曳速度外转向时必须始终加油门"]}}],"expected":{"acceptable_skills":["product_support"],"required_tools":[],"risk_level":"low","approval_required":false,"handoff_required":false,"min_evidence_count":1,"answer_must_contain":["转向需要油门"],"answer_must_not_contain":[]},"golden_answer":"转向需要油门动力，除拖曳速度外，转向时必须始终加油门；松开油门后转向能力会迅速下降。","session_id":null,"user_id":null,"images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["转向需要油门动力","除拖曳速度外转向时必须始终加油门"],"manual_dir":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册"},"notes":""}
{"case_id":"product_support_025","category":"product_support","message":"摩托艇从全速停下大概要多远？","turns":[{"message":"摩托艇从全速停下大概要多远？","images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["完全停止的距离约为90米","受总重量、水面状况和风向影响"]}}],"expected":{"acceptable_skills":["product_support"],"required_tools":[],"risk_level":"low","approval_required":false,"handoff_required":false,"min_evidence_count":1,"answer_must_contain":["90 米"],"answer_must_not_contain":[]},"golden_answer":"手册给出的参考是从全速松油门或熄火后，靠水阻完全停止距离约 90 米，具体会受重量、风向和水面影响。","session_id":null,"user_id":null,"images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["完全停止的距离约为90米","受总重量、水面状况和风向影响"],"manual_dir":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册"},"notes":""}
{"case_id":"product_support_026","category":"product_support","message":"摩托艇穿越尾流时怎么做？","turns":[{"message":"摩托艇穿越尾流时怎么做？","images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["减速并斜切尾流","不要将下巴或胸部贴近车把驾驶"]}}],"expected":{"acceptable_skills":["product_support"],"required_tools":[],"risk_level":"low","approval_required":false,"handoff_required":false,"min_evidence_count":1,"answer_must_contain":["斜切","尾流"],"answer_must_not_contain":[]},"golden_answer":"穿越尾流或浪涌时要先减速，再以一定角度斜切过去；不要把下巴或胸部贴近车把，并始终紧握车把、双脚放在脚坑底板上。","session_id":null,"user_id":null,"images":[],"metadata":{"source_manual":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册/摩托艇手册.txt","source_facts":["减速并斜切尾流","不要将下巴或胸部贴近车把驾驶"],"manual_dir":"/Users/nikonzhang/compeletion/手册"},"notes":""}
